---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
import gbpImg from '@/assets/images/LS - google business.png';
---

<Layout
  title="Google Business Profile | Presencia Digital"
  description="Optimizamos tu perfil de Google para mejorar la visibilidad local con información completa, actualizada y confiable."
>
  <div class="gbp-page">

    <!-- BREADCRUMB -->
    <nav class="gbp-breadcrumb container-libera" aria-label="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/soluciones">Soluciones</a>
      <span>›</span>
      <a href="/soluciones/presencia-digital">Presencia Digital</a>
      <span>›</span>
      <span aria-current="page">Google Business Profile</span>
    </nav>

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="gbp-hero">
      <div class="container-libera gbp-hero-grid">

        <div class="gbp-hero-copy">
          <h1 class="gbp-title">
            Google Business Profile: <em>que te encuentren cuando alguien ya está buscando</em> lo que haces.
          </h1>
          <p class="gbp-lead">
            Optimizamos tu perfil de Google para que tu negocio aparezca en búsquedas locales con información completa, actualizada y pensada para generar confianza antes del primer clic.
          </p>
        </div>

        <aside class="gbp-mock">
          <Image
            src={gbpImg}
            alt="Google Business Profile — LIBERA Studio"
            widths={[600, 1000]}
            sizes="(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 50vw"
            format="webp"
            quality={78}
            loading="eager"
            fetchpriority="high"
            class="gbp-hero-img"
          />
        </aside>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CONTENT -->
    <section class="gbp-content">
      <div class="container-libera gbp-content-grid">

        <div class="gbp-body">
          <div class="gbp-hl-block">
            <div class="gbp-hl-icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="11" cy="11" r="8"/><line x1="21" y1="21" x2="16.65" y2="16.65"/></svg>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p>Cuando alguien busca "dentista cerca de mí", "taller mecánico en Mérida" o "contador en la colonia Centro", Google muestra nombre, fotos, horarios, reseñas y formas de contacto.</p>
              <p class="gbp-orange"><strong>En ese momento, la decisión empieza antes de entrar a tu sitio.</strong></p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <p>Un perfil incompleto, sin fotos reales, con horarios desactualizados o pocas reseñas puede hacer que el cliente elija a otro negocio. Un perfil bien trabajado transmite actividad, confianza y claridad desde el primer resultado.</p>

          <div class="gbp-quote-block">
            <div class="gbp-q-icon">
              <svg width="22" height="22" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
            </div>
            <p>Eso no depende solo de la suerte. Depende de tener una ficha bien configurada: <strong>categorías correctas, descripción clara, servicios completos, imágenes reales, respuestas a reseñas</strong> y actualizaciones periódicas que muestran que el negocio está activo.</p>
          </div>

          <p>Configuramos tu perfil desde cero o auditamos el que ya tienes. Identificamos qué está faltando, qué puede mejorar y lo dejamos listo para competir mejor en búsquedas locales. Después te enseñamos a mantenerlo o lo gestionamos nosotros como parte de tu presencia digital.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gbp-checklist">
          <h2 class="gbp-cl-title">Lo que hacemos</h2>
          <ul class="gbp-cl-list">
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M9 11l3 3L22 4"/><path d="M21 12v7a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h11"/></svg>
              <span>Configuración completa o auditoría del perfil existente.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20.59 13.41l-7.17 7.17a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0L2 12V2h10l8.59 8.59a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.82z"/><line x1="7" y1="7" x2="7.01" y2="7"/></svg>
              <span>Selección de categoría principal y categorías secundarias correctas.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M12 20h9"/><path d="M16.5 3.5a2.121 2.121 0 0 1 3 3L7 19l-4 1 1-4L16.5 3.5z"/></svg>
              <span>Redacción de descripción optimizada para búsqueda local.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/></svg>
              <span>Carga y organización de imágenes del negocio, equipo y servicios.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
              <span>Configuración de horarios, servicios, atributos y preguntas frecuentes.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><polygon points="12 2 15.09 8.26 22 9.27 17 14.14 18.18 21.02 12 17.77 5.82 21.02 7 14.14 2 9.27 8.91 8.26 12 2"/></svg>
              <span>Estrategia de respuesta a reseñas para construir reputación.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg>
              <span>Seguimiento mensual de métricas: vistas, clics, llamadas y solicitudes de ruta.</span>
            </li>
            <li class="gbp-cl-item">
              <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><line x1="12" y1="8" x2="12" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="16" x2="12.01" y2="16"/></svg>
              <span>Recomendaciones para mantener el perfil activo y competitivo.</span>
            </li>
          </ul>
        </div>

      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <section class="gbp-cta">
      <div class="container-libera gbp-cta-inner">
        <div class="gbp-cta-left">
          <div class="gbp-pin-icon" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg width="52" height="52" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none">
              <path d="M32 6C20.95 6 12 14.95 12 26c0 14 20 32 20 32s20-18 20-32C52 14.95 43.05 6 32 6z" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
              <circle cx="32" cy="26" r="7" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" fill="none"/>
              <path d="M20 58c-2 2-5 3.5-8 3.5 0-3 1.5-6 3.5-8" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
              <path d="M44 58c2 2 5 3.5 8 3.5 0-3-1.5-6-3.5-8" stroke="#f77f00" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <div class="gbp-cta-text">
            <p>Aparecer en Google cuando alguien ya está buscando lo que ofreces puede convertirse en uno de los canales más directos para</p>
            <p class="gbp-orange">generar llamadas, visitas y solicitudes reales.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <a href="/diagnostico" class="btn-primary gbp-cta-btn">Optimizar mi perfil de Google <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>

  <style>
    .gbp-page { background: #ffffff; color: var(--text-primary); }

    /* ── BREADCRUMB ── */
    .gbp-breadcrumb {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding-top: calc(var(--nav-height) + 1.25rem);
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
    }
    .gbp-breadcrumb a { color: var(--text-secondary); transition: color 0.2s; }
    .gbp-breadcrumb a:hover { color: #f77f00; }
    .gbp-breadcrumb [aria-current="page"] { color: #f77f00; font-weight: 600; }

    /* ── HERO ── */
    .gbp-hero {
      padding-top: clamp(4rem, calc(3vw + 2.5rem), 5rem);
      padding-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
    }
    .gbp-hero-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
      gap: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 4rem);
      align-items: start;
    }


    .gbp-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 3.2vw, 2.75rem);
      line-height: 1.1;
      letter-spacing: -0.02em;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      color: var(--text-primary);
    }
    .gbp-title em { font-style: normal; color: #f77f00; }

    .gbp-lead {
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      line-height: 1.75;
      max-width: 46ch;
    }

    /* ── MOCK ── */
    .gbp-mock {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
    }

    .gbp-hero-img {
      width: 100%;
      height: auto;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      display: block;
    }

    /* GBP Card (unused — kept as dead code; will be removed) */
    .gbp-card {
      background: #ffffff;
      border: 1px solid #dadce0;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
      box-shadow: 0 2px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.14);
    }

    .gbp-card-photos {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 0.55fr;
      height: 6.5rem;
      gap: 2px;
      background: #dadce0;
    }
    .gbp-photo-main {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003049 0%, #1a5a7a 100%);
    }
    .gbp-photo-col {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-rows: 1fr 1fr;
      gap: 2px;
    }
    .gbp-photo-sm {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #b0cad4 0%, #8fb8c8 100%);
    }
    .gbp-photo-more {
      background: rgba(0, 48, 73, 0.68);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .gbp-photo-more span {
      font-size: 0.44rem;
      color: #ffffff;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.3;
      padding: 0 0.15rem;
    }

    .gbp-card-body {
      padding: 0.6rem 0.7rem;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.25rem;
    }

    .gbp-biz-name { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.72rem; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0; }

    .gbp-stars-row { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.25rem; }
    .gbp-rating { font-weight: 700; font-size: 0.62rem; color: #1a1a1a; }
    .gbp-stars { font-size: 0.6rem; color: #f9ab00; }
    .gbp-reviews { font-size: 0.55rem; color: #1a73e8; }

    .gbp-category { font-size: 0.55rem; color: #5f6368; margin: 0; }

    .gbp-actions {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      margin: 0.2rem 0;
    }
    .gbp-action {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.2rem;
      flex: 1;
      padding: 0.25rem 0.1rem;
      border: 1px solid #dadce0;
      border-radius: 0.25rem;
    }
    .gbp-action span { font-size: 0.4rem; color: #1a73e8; text-align: center; }

    .gbp-info { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.2rem; }
    .gbp-info-row {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      font-size: 0.5rem;
      color: #5f6368;
      line-height: 1.4;
    }
    .gbp-info-row svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.05rem; }
    .gbp-open { color: #188038; font-weight: 600; }

    /* Phone */
    .gbp-phone {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .gbp-phone-frame {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 9rem;
      background: #1a1a1a;
      border-radius: 1rem;
      padding: 0.5rem 0.3rem 0.6rem;
      box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0,0,0,0.28);
      position: relative;
    }
    .gbp-phone-notch {
      width: 2.5rem;
      height: 0.35rem;
      background: #333;
      border-radius: 999px;
      margin: 0 auto 0.4rem;
    }
    .gbp-phone-screen {
      background: #ffffff;
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .gbp-serp-bar {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.3rem;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.4rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .gbp-g { font-weight: 900; font-size: 0.7rem; color: #4285f4; line-height: 1; }
    .gbp-serp-input {
      flex: 1;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.15rem 0.35rem;
      border: 1px solid #dfe1e5;
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 0.42rem;
      color: #5f6368;
    }

    .gbp-serp-tabs {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0;
      padding: 0.15rem 0.4rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .gbp-tab-a { font-size: 0.42rem; color: #1a73e8; padding: 0.15rem 0.3rem; border-bottom: 2px solid #1a73e8; }
    .gbp-tab-i { font-size: 0.42rem; color: #5f6368; padding: 0.15rem 0.3rem; }

    .gbp-serp-label { font-size: 0.44rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; padding: 0.25rem 0.4rem 0; margin: 0; }

    .gbp-serp-map {
      height: 3.2rem;
      background: #e8f0e8;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
      margin: 0.1rem 0;
    }
    .gbp-smap-road { position: absolute; background: #ffffff; }
    .gbp-smap-h { height: 4px; top: 50%; left: 0; right: 0; }
    .gbp-smap-v { width: 4px; left: 40%; top: 0; bottom: 0; }
    .gbp-smap-pin { position: absolute; }
    .gbp-smap-pin-r { top: 22%; left: 36%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
    .gbp-smap-pin-g { top: 55%; left: 62%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }
    .gbp-smap-pin-g2 { top: 35%; left: 72%; transform: translate(-50%, -50%); }

    .gbp-lr {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 0.3rem 0.4rem;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f0f0f0;
    }
    .gbp-lr:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .gbp-lr-active { background: #fefaf6; }

    .gbp-lr-info { flex: 1; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.1rem; }
    .gbp-lr-name { font-size: 0.5rem; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0; }
    .gbp-lr-stars2 { font-size: 0.44rem; color: #f9ab00; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 0.15rem; }
    .gbp-lr-stars2 span { color: #5f6368; }
    .gbp-lr-stars2-g { color: #ccc; }
    .gbp-lr-meta { font-size: 0.42rem; color: #5f6368; margin: 0; }
    .gbp-lr-btns {
      display: flex;
      gap: 0.2rem;
      margin-top: 0.15rem;
    }
    .gbp-lr-btns span {
      font-size: 0.38rem;
      color: #1a73e8;
      border: 1px solid #1a73e8;
      border-radius: 999px;
      padding: 0.1rem 0.25rem;
    }

    .gbp-lr-thumb {
      width: 2rem;
      height: 2rem;
      border-radius: 0.2rem;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #003049, #1a5a7a);
    }
    .gbp-lr-thumb-g { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ccc, #aaa); }

    /* ── CONTENT ── */
    .gbp-content {
      padding-top: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      padding-bottom: clamp(2.5rem, 5vw, 4rem);
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .gbp-content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
      gap: clamp(2rem, 5vw, 5rem);
      align-items: start;
    }

    .gbp-body { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 1.1rem; }
    .gbp-body p { color: var(--text-secondary); font-size: 0.95rem; line-height: 1.75; margin: 0; }

    .gbp-orange { color: #f77f00 !important; font-weight: 600 !important; }

    .gbp-hl-block {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      border-left: 3px solid #f77f00;
      background: #fef9f5;
    }
    .gbp-hl-icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem; }
    .gbp-hl-block p { font-size: 0.92rem !important; line-height: 1.6 !important; margin: 0; }

    .gbp-quote-block {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      padding: 0.9rem 1rem;
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.4rem;
    }
    .gbp-q-icon { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem; }
    .gbp-quote-block p { font-size: 0.9rem; line-height: 1.65; color: var(--text-secondary); margin: 0; }
    .gbp-quote-block strong { color: var(--text-primary); }

    /* Checklist */
    .gbp-cl-title {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(1rem, 1.6vw, 1.25rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: #f77f00;
      margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
    .gbp-cl-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--border); }

    .gbp-cl-list { list-style: none; margin: 0; padding: 0; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0; }

    .gbp-cl-item {
      display: flex;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 0.65rem;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      color: var(--text-secondary);
      line-height: 1.5;
      padding: 0.7rem 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
    }
    .gbp-cl-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
    .gbp-cl-item svg { flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 0.1rem; }

    /* ── CTA ── */
    .gbp-cta {
      padding-top: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      padding-bottom: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.5rem);
      background: var(--surface-alt);
    }
    .gbp-cta-inner {
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: space-between;
      gap: 2rem;
      padding: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
      border: 1px solid var(--border);
      border-radius: 0.5rem;
      background: #ffffff;
    }
    .gbp-cta-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 1.5rem; }
    .gbp-pin-icon { flex-shrink: 0; }
    .gbp-cta-text { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 0.3rem; }
    .gbp-cta-text p {
      font-family: var(--font-display);
      font-size: clamp(0.9rem, 1.3vw, 1.05rem);
      font-weight: 700;
      color: var(--text-primary);
      line-height: 1.35;
      margin: 0;
    }
    .gbp-cta-btn {
      white-space: nowrap;
      flex-shrink: 0;
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.5rem;
      padding: 0.85rem 1.5rem;
      font-size: 0.92rem;
    }

    /* ── RESPONSIVE ── */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .gbp-hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
      .gbp-content-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    }
    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .gbp-cta-inner { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; }
      .gbp-cta-btn { width: 100%; justify-content: center; }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>
